{"tid":2201266,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［只差一點點］成龍拍戲遇意外跌落水 消失45秒唐季禮擔心到喊","createTime":"2020-09-13T16:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T16:27:19.000Z","uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"09b064b05755eddec1aa0570bef9446ccd846e6c","tid":2201266,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLveKuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLveKuq.jpg&h=353b077a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日頻頻為新戲宣傳的成龍，在接受訪問時提到為《急》拍攝海上戲時發生意外。從短片所見，駕着快艇的成龍載着女主角母其彌雅，連人帶艇撞到海中的大石後快艇隨即翻側，而成龍及母其彌雅亦雙雙跌落水，但兩人落水後只見到迅速已浮上水母其彌雅一臉茫然，過幾秒後她即捉實快艇控制杆，但同樣跌落水的成龍卻不知所踪，此時正在附近預備的救援人員亦隨即趕到，在快艇另一邊找回成龍。對於差點被浸死，成龍憶述說：「船一翻把我吸到水底，我的經驗就是那個急流把我一吸的時候，我跟自己講『不要怕』，我也忘了那個情況，好像有神力助我一樣，我慢慢起來推着那個船推推推。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZymMok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZymMok&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8Fuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=b52fc1b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZymMok</a>"},{"pid":"f47de92c66ffd65240b91c1650468df9ea2c5869","tid":2201266,"uid":11291,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"點解救得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361076fe85681e633fb0b50aecf5c472dd155538","tid":2201266,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"死唔去真係無天理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b65d91d79945fec471e5e4a7e9801666950a11","tid":2201266,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔係植物人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b87fc874ff47e35e8c1f529036ffb17bf2e5957","tid":2201266,"uid":258899,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"以為係話條女係女主角母親其彌雅